ually found under dense vegetation or in branches no higher than 2 metres (6.6 ft) off the ground. Behavior Males are territorial, being found either on their own or as part of a pair with a female. Females are typically only found paired with a male. The species has been observed to have three different kinds of call - a \"kreew\" sound, which probably serves as a sort of contact call, an alarm call, and the song. Only females sing. Distribution is usually about 0.49 individuals per hectare. Conservation status The Boa Nova tapaculo is estimated to consist of no more than 2,883 individuals, and is threatened by logging and deforestation, resulting in the scientists who described it urging that it be classified as an endangered species on the IUCN Red List. References Data related to Scytalopus gonzagai at Wikispecies", "shortSummary": "The Boa Nova tapaculo (Scytalopus gonzagai), also known as the Bahian mouse-colored tapaculo, is a species of passerine bird native to Bahi…", "locations": ["巴伊亞州", "科学美国人", "大西洋沿岸森林", "阿拉塔卡", "博阿诺瓦", "伊瓜伊"], "threats": ["森林砍伐"], "lat": -12.0, "lng": -41.0, "imageUrl": "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/de/Scytalopus_gonzagai_by_Thomaz_de_Carvalho_Callado.jpg/960px-Scytalopus_gonzagai_by_Thomaz_de_Carvalho_Callado.jpg", "kingdomId": "taxonomy-kingdom-animalia", "phylumId": "taxonomy-phylum-chordata", "classId": "taxonomy-class-aves", "genusId": "taxonomy-genus-scytalopus", "speciesId": "taxonomy-species-scytalopus-gonzagai", "taxonomyIds": {"kingdom": "taxonomy-kingdom-animalia", "phylum": "taxonomy-phylum-chordata", "class": "taxonomy-class-aves", "genus": "taxonomy-genus-scytalopus", "species": "taxonomy-species-scytalopus-gonzagai"}, "expandable": true, "x": -468.61, "y": 162.36, "z": -331.52}, {"id": "taxonomy-genus-scytalopus", "name": "Scytalopus", "latinName": "Scytalopus", "type": "taxonomy", "taxonomyLevel": "genus", "summary": "Scytalopus（Scytalopus）是图谱中的分类级分类节点，当前关联49种鸟类，如Marsh tapaculo、Diamantina tapaculo、Brasília tapaculo等49种鸟类。", "expandable": true, "memberCount": 49, "x": 8.34, "y": 664.11, "z": -48.36}], "links": [{"key": "bird-boa-nova-tapaculo-614d1c0b__belongs_to_species__taxonomy-species-scytalopus-gonzagai", "source": "bird-boa-nova-tapaculo-614d1c0b", "target": "taxonomy-species-scytalopus-gonzagai", "relation": "belongs_to_species", "label": "属于种", "evidence": "依据 birds.csv 中的种字段补充。"}, {"key": "taxonomy-species-scytalopus-gonzagai__belongs_to_genus__taxonomy-genus-scytalopus", "source": "taxonomy-species-scytalopus-gonzagai", "target": "taxonomy-genus-scytalopus", "relation": "belongs_to_genus", "label": "属于属", "evidence": "依据 birds.csv 分类字段补充：Boa Nova tapaculo 属于属 Scytalopus。"}]}
